title: The Cult--Sonic Temple (1989)--vikingsfreak
description:
Sonic Temple is the fourth album by the The Cult, released in 1989. The album was certified Platinum by the RIAA in 1993. Sonic Temple was the last album recorded with long time bassist Jamie Stewart.
